{"questionId":"9074985","questionHtml":"<p>Six identical capacitors, each of value <em>C</em>, are connected as shown.</p>\n<p><img src=\"__IMG__/869f56d775ee96781d7790843a61f5e7edcf7f6f.png\"></p>\n<p>What is the total capacitance?</p>\n<p>A.&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{C}{6}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mi>C</mi>\n    <mn>6</mn>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span></p>\n<p>B.&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{{2C}}{3}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>2</mn>\n      <mi>C</mi>\n    </mrow>\n    <mn>3</mn>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span></p>\n<p>C.&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{{3C}}{3}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>3</mn>\n      <mi>C</mi>\n    </mrow>\n    <mn>3</mn>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span></p>\n<p>D. 6<em>C</em></p>","markschemeHtml":"<p>B</p>","meta":{"questionId":"9074985","referenceCode":"17N.1.HL.TZ0.37","subjectId":"46-dp-physics-last-assessment-2024","title":"Six identical capacitors, each of value C, are connected as shown. What is the total capacitance? A. C 6 B. 2 C 3 C. 3 C 3 D. 6C","paper":"1","level":"HL","questionNumber":"37","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 1]","breadcrumbLabels":["Additional higher level (AHL)","Additional higher level (AHL)","Topic 11: Electromagnetic induction","11.3 – Capacitance","Additional higher level (AHL)","Topic 11: Electromagnetic induction"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}},"schemaVersion":2}